trans-unit.source: Represents a design-time editor sheet for the properties of a <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression in the UI of a designer host at design time.
trans-unit.target: Representerar ett blad för designtid Redigeraren för egenskaperna för en <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> uttryck i Användargränssnittet för en designer värd i designläge.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor> class together with the RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet class to select the individual properties of a `RouteUrl` expression, and to combine the selected expression property values into a `RouteUrl` expression.
trans-unit.target: Den visuella designern använder den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor>klassen tillsammans med klassen RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet att välja enskilda egenskaper för en `RouteUrl` uttryck, och att kombinera värdena för valda uttryck i en `RouteUrl` uttryck.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method returns a RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden returnerar ett RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet-objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In the expressions dialog box, when you select a control property and bind it to a `RouteUrl` expression, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: I dialogrutan uttryck när du väljer en egenskapskontroll och Binder det till en `RouteUrl` uttryck, visuell designer anropar den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the returned RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet object to prompt for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Den visuella frågedesignern används returnerade RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet objektet för att fråga efter den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>och <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: Once the properties are selected, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A> method to combine the properties into a `RouteUrl` expression string.
trans-unit.target: När egenskaperna väljs den visuella designern anropar den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>metod för att kombinera egenskaper i en `RouteUrl` uttryckssträng.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> property must be specified if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property is not specified.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>egenskapen måste anges om den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>egenskapen inte har angetts.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property must be specified if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> is not specified.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>egenskapen måste anges om den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>har inte angetts.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Both properties may be specified.
trans-unit.target: Båda egenskaperna kan anges.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The initial <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property values are set using the input `expression` string.
trans-unit.target: Första <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>och <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>egenskapsvärden konfigureras med hjälp av indata `expression` sträng.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A> property is set using the input `serviceProvider` implementation.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>-egenskapen anges med hjälp av indata `serviceProvider` implementering.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>

trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om den <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> uttryckssträng är giltig.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string is valid; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
